    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Style and culture of an ethnic group of central Peru, in the Valle del Mantaro. They probably originated in the Huari culture.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
